data.description: This remarkable home offers a prime location on Big Coppitt Key, perfectly situated for both work and play in Key West. With its convenient proximity to Key West and Boca Chica Navy Base, this turnkey 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath home presents an excellent opportunity for those seeking a low-maintenance lifestyle in a tropical paradise. Also makes a great vacation rental for those looking to enjoy Key West.The exterior of the property boasts hardiplank siding, impact windows and doors, aluminum railing, and a fresh coat of paint throughout. The addition of new LED lighting, outlets, and covers enhances the overall appeal of the home. Notably, this property is wind-rated to 180 mph, making it exceptionally resilient, and is located above the flood zone, resulting in lower flood insurance costs.This energy-efficient home also offers the advantage of reduced monthly costs. Upon entering, one is immediately struck by the inviting and relaxed ambiance of the living area, seamlessly flowing into a well-designed kitchen. Upstairs, the residence provides a haven for relaxation, featuring a guest bedroom, a spacious main bedroom suite, and a full-sized bathroom.Outside, the property is embraced by a protective courtyard, creating a private retreat. The addition of a rear pergola offers a delightful space for outdoor leisure activities. Furthermore, the ample covered parking ensures convenience and protection for vehicles.In summary, this exceptional MLS listing is an enticing opportunity for those seeking a well-located, low-maintenance home in a tropical setting. The combination of its desirable features, including its ideal location, updated exterior, energy efficiency, and inviting interior spaces, make this property a must-see. Don't miss your chance to view and secure this remarkable home today!
